    Get adjusted fvps for particular touchstone and vaccine delivery methods

    get_fvps.Rd

    Get adjusted fvps for particular touchstone and vaccine delivery methods

    get_fvps(
  con,
  touchstone,
  baseline_vaccine_delivery,
  focal_vaccine_delivery,
  focal_scenario_type,
  countries = NULL,
  vaccination_years = NULL
)

    Arguments

    con

    DB connection

    baseline_vaccine_delivery

    A list of lists containing vaccine and activity_type (routine or campaign) describing delivery

    focal_vaccine_delivery

    A list of lists containing vaccine and activity_type (routine or campaign) describing delivery

    focal_scenario_type

    A character determining from which scenario_type coverage estimates shall be extracted

    countries

    Optional vector of countries to filter data

    vaccination_years

    Option vector of years to filter data

    touchtonse

    Touchstone to get data for

    Value

    Tibble containing fvp data
